title: Rams Win Super Bowl LVI
description:
Jalen & Jacoby breakdown all the angles from the Rams dramatic Super Bowl win over Bengals, plus the guys discuss Matthew Stafford’s legacy, Cooper Kupp’s incredible season, Sean McVay's play-calling, celebrate Aaron Donald’s dominance, rank the halftime show and give Valentine's Day advice!!!
